snippet.title: Cook For The Giant (VR) - Summer #UE4jam Submission
snippet.description:
We made this VR game over the course of five days during the Unreal Engine Summer Jam 29.07.2017 - 4.07.2017 with a subset of our team.

Download and more information: https://vhiterabbit.itch.io/cook-for-the-giant
